# 5. Operating Principles

VELOX X-22 is built around five primary principles:

### Engine Pre-Compression

Part of engine output is directed into hydraulic storage.

### Pressure Buffering

Energy is temporarily accumulated.

### Controlled Release

Pressure is released strategically.

### Rotational Amplification

Stored pressure contributes to output torque.

### Load Balancing

System continuously adjusts to resistance changes.

